data.value: Plucky penguins Skipper, Kowalski, Rico and Private the most elite spies ever hatched join forces with a chic undercover organization known as the North Wind. Led by highly trained, handsome and arrogant Agent Classified, this special inter- species task force must stop a many-tentacled villain, Dr. Octavius Brine, from destroying the world.
